SUMMARY:[Federal Practice Areas] The CFPB Works To Ensure Bilt Consumers A
 re Made Whole
DESCRIPTION:The CFPB has been working to ensure consumers affected by Bilt
 ’s transition to a new bank partner are appropriately remedied. CFPB off
 icials met with Bilt to understand the issues caused by the transition and
  what steps Bilt has taken to ensure customers affected by challenges with
  the transition were made whole.\nhttps://www.consumerfinance.gov/about-us
 /newsroom/the-cfpb-works-to-ensure-bilt-consumers-are-made-whole/
URL:https://www.consumerfinance.gov/about-us/newsroom/the-cfpb-works-to-en
 sure-bilt-consumers-are-made-whole/
