DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20251215
SUMMARY:[Federal Practice Areas] Agencies Announce Dollar Thresholds for S
 maller Loan Exemption from Appraisal Requirements for Higher-priced Mortga
 ge Loans
DESCRIPTION:The CFPB\, FRB\, and OCC are announcing that the 2026 threshol
 d for higher-priced mortgage loans that are subject to special appraisal r
 equirements will increase from $33\,500 to $34\,200.\nhttps://www.consumer
 finance.gov/about-us/newsroom/agencies-announce-dollar-thresholds-for-smal
 ler-loan-exemption-from-appraisal-requirements-for-higher-priced-mortgage-
 loans-2025/
URL:https://www.consumerfinance.gov/about-us/newsroom/agencies-announce-do
 llar-thresholds-for-smaller-loan-exemption-from-appraisal-requirements-for
 -higher-priced-mortgage-loans-2025/
CATEGORIES:Federal Practice Areas
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
