 international remittance company Wise resolving claims including advertisi
 ng inaccurate fees and failing to properly disclose exchange rates and oth
 er costs.\nhttps://www.consumerfinance.gov/about-us/newsroom/cfpb-amends-w
 ise-order-for-remittance-practices/
